From: Paul Cercueil <paul@crapouillou.net>
Date: Sat, 31 May 2025 13:58:19 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] download prerequisites with curl

wget does not support FTP anymore.

Signed-off-by: Paul Cercueil <paul@crapouillou.net>
---
 contrib/download_prerequisites | 6 +-----
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 5 deletions(-)

diff --git a/contrib/download_prerequisites b/contrib/download_prerequisites
index b50f47c..62bc603 100755
--- a/contrib/download_prerequisites
+++ b/contrib/download_prerequisites
@@ -55,11 +55,7 @@ case $OS in
   ;;
 esac
 
-if type wget > /dev/null ; then
-  fetch='wget'
-else
-  fetch='curl -LO -u anonymous:'
-fi
+fetch='curl -LO -u anonymous:'
 chksum_extension='sha512'
 directory='.'
 
